            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"領土、北約、資產、赦免……全文閱讀美俄提出的28點烏克蘭和平計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"641\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Dx381zS6TGWuASWcLgTkGg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/2f8418b0-c751-11f0-98f7-882b961128b0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">領土、北約、資產、赦免……全文閱讀美俄提出的28點烏克蘭和平計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
